snippet.title: Pig Rush 1.2 update - Bees and giant pigs
snippet.description:
Video demonstrating the latest update to the iPhone/iPod Touch game Pig Rush. New features include: bees that mark other player scores, local/global scores, stats, Twitter support, Challenge (email), and CRAZY BIG PIG!

Also available on Android!

http://www.pigrush.com
